    <div class="welcome2">
        <p class="lead">We're just regular people who care about regular people.</p>
        <p> Conation is an app developed by four BCIT computing students, brought together by fate as "DTC Team 08".</p>
        <p> COVID-19 has uprooted the daily lives of everyone, including us. Being computing students, it was easy for us to
