            energetic and enthusiastic students have each other to rely on, but we know that is not the case for everyone. 
            And we also know it's even harder for people with more at stake during this pandemic. </p>
        <p> Conation strives to help friends, family, colleagues and neighbours. We're focused on supporting the economy
            through the people most vulnerable; the people we hold closest to us.</p>
